cross: Paphiopedilum liemianum x Paphiopedilum Avalon Magic

measurements.description: One flower and two buds on a 16.0-cm slightly arching inflorescence; dorsal sepal green, veined cordovan, wide white margin; synsepal pale green, veined darker green; petals hirsute, twisted, slightly reflexed, pale green spotted oxblood; pouch pale green, overlaid rose, stippled darker rose; staminode largely green, centrally lighter, margin velvet, tinted cordovan; substance firm; texture waxy.
